  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Let’s join the birds and transform the deserted island into your own unique garden!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The birds bring plants and decorations to turn the barren land into a paradise of your creation.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>In this garden, you’ll find:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 30 types of「Birds」 to deliver gifts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant seeds and collect over 150 unique「plants」</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase over 400「decorations」 to customize your space</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 60「Sprites」 with their「 exclusive cabins」</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No tasks—just pure「freedom」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/82af2c55076b23e157abbeb0e312a21d.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/82af2c55076b23e157abbeb0e312a21d.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/82af2c55076b23e157abbeb0e312a21d.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What do the birds bring?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You might get seeds, gifts… or maybe even bird poop?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whatever it is, it can become part of your garden! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place items on the ground, watch seeds grow, unwrap gifts… then arrange everything however you like!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3b736e3ea173a8502634eb635870115a.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3b736e3ea173a8502634eb635870115a.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3b736e3ea173a8502634eb635870115a.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mysterious Seeds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What will sprout? A flower? A tree? Or maybe a mushroom!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some plants might surprise you—or even disappoint. No worries! Sell them if you’d like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Don’t feel bad—the plants won’t cry… but we, the creators, might ;_;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3159b2bdba35921bac9f4fd9e465db21.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3159b2bdba35921bac9f4fd9e465db21.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3159b2bdba35921bac9f4fd9e465db21.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Magic Crate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This crate transforms anything into star coins!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s linked to another realm—toss items in, and they’ll turn into currency.<br>(<i>Except Sprites.</i> They hate it here.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/aab9c3ceb28ed4108d33dadbb1aa486c.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/aab9c3ceb28ed4108d33dadbb1aa486c.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/aab9c3ceb28ed4108d33dadbb1aa486c.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Sprites and Their Island</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The bird on the crate recycles star coins… which means it SELLS stuff.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why does a bird sell things? Why does it have an interdimensional backpack? And why are Sprites inside?<br>Don’t ask questions—just buy the Sprites!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/cbc64108ff6c68f683d20a70be6bcd2f.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/cbc64108ff6c68f683d20a70be6bcd2f.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/cbc64108ff6c68f683d20a70be6bcd2f.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enjoy Your Freedom</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No tasks, no exclamation marks, no final boss… you’re FREE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This isn’t like other games—<strong>you decide what to do!</strong><br>Collect everything, design themed gardens, or just stare at birds. It’s up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/93f2e15c785ed4889d02e101d9245278.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/93f2e15c785ed4889d02e101d9245278.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/93f2e15c785ed4889d02e101d9245278.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Contact Us</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Email: <a href=\"mailto:982445535@qq.com\">982445535@qq.com</a></strong></p>",
